Coming Out - Program 2: Becoming A Man (with Mike Carducci) - This is program 2 of a 13-part series produced by White Horse Media entitled, "Coming Out: Former Gays Testify of God’s Saving Love." In program 2, Steve Wohlberg interviews former gay Mike Carducci. Homosexuality, gays, straights, love, God, sin, sex are all discussed. Order the "Coming Out" series today!

The entire 13-part "Coming Out" series is available on DVD here: http://whitehorsemedia.com/store/40-homosexuality/112-coming-out-former-gays-testify-of-gods-saving-love.html. Order online or call 208-448-4446.
